          <title>iOS 18.4: Apple's Latest Software Update Brings New Emojis and Features</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Apple has released its iOS 18.4 software update, which includes eight new emojis. The new features also bring a new Photos tool and Ambient Music feature to the iPhone.]]></description>
