          <title>Tesla's Range-Extending Battery Pack for Cybertruck Disappears from Online Store</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Tesla's range-extending battery pack for the Cybertruck has vanished from the company's online store, sparking speculation that it may have been canceled. The pack was designed to boost the electric pickup's range to over 500 miles but delivered only around 350 miles in reality.]]></description>
